          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Restoring the Armed Career Criminal Act</b></p> <p>This bill modifies the prior convictions that trigger a 15-year enhanced mandatory minimum prison term for a defendant who commits a firearms offense after three or more such prior convictions.</p>]]></text>
